{
  "stem": "3820.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not as a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not as-- you know, prior to 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If there was any, I, being a child, was not aware of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing of-- of terrible consequences.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always, you know, the name-calling and the things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was never told of anything that was really extremely serious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember the bombing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My aunt Frances and her husband and child had-- were living in France at the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had come to visit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were going on one of our picnics when the planes came out of the sky.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember it turning black.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the bombs started to fall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And within hours, our town was burning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were in the fields, high, you know, by the road in ditches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after that, we gathered in I don't know whose house it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe it was my grandfather's.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But most of the town was in ruins and burning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] life changed after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was September 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it changed because we were confined to a certain area almost immediately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The freedom that I had had before didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't go back to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were-- the grown-ups seemed to be changed in a way that filtered through to the children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They started-- my uncles, especially my uncle Chaim, wanted to leave German-occupied Poland to go across to the part that the Russians occupied.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was decided that part of the family would go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The older people didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of my aunts had a newborn child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the family split.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
